text: The Gyeonggi Provincial Office of Education is the office of education for Gyeonggi Province, South Korea. The school's superintendent is Yim Tae-hee. It was established in 1956. == Superintendent == The school's superintendent is Yim Tae-hee. He became the superintendent in 2022 July. == References == Category:Schools in South Korea Category:1956 establishments in Asia Category:1950s establishments in South Korea
title: Gyeonggi Provincial Office of Education
